data.description: Welcome to this stunning end unit townhome, boasting a spacious 2,119 square feet of living space, and guess what – it's practically brand new! As an added bonus, it's an end unit, offering you extra privacy and natural light. Constructed in 2021, this home embodies contemporary living with its thoughtfully designed open-concept layout on the main floor.    The heart of the home is the generously sized kitchen area, complete with a large island, gleaming stainless steel appliances, and elegant granite countertops. Convenience is key with a half bath on the main level, and the sliding door leads to a screened-in lanai, perfect for enjoying the outdoors while staying sheltered. Plus, there's a handy storage closet for all your essentials, and the backyard is enclosed by a fence for added privacy and security.    Ascending the stairs, you'll find a spacious master bedroom that promises restful nights. It features a roomy walk-in closet, while the master bathroom is a retreat in itself, boasting both a shower and a separate tub, along with double sinks for your comfort. Two additional bedrooms on this level offer ample space, with one of them also featuring a walk-in closet, making storage a breeze.    This community offers a wealth of amenities for your enjoyment, adding to the appeal of this fantastic home. Whether it's a dip in the pool, a game of tennis, or a leisurely stroll in well-manicured surroundings, you'll find plenty to relish.    Don't miss your chance to experience the charm and convenience of this beautiful townhome. Call today to schedule your private viewing and take the first step toward making this house your cherished home.
